The Developer: Kilpep Development Limited

The executives behind Kilpep Developments have more than 20 years of experience in the construction sector. Currently, the company maintains a delivery pace of approximately 20 homes per month for the social and affordable sector, demonstrating proven operational and financial capacity in projects of similar scale.

In summary, the Bettystown opportunity offers investors the chance to participate in a project with an LTV of 53%, backed by physical assets in a high-demand location and managed by a development team with an impeccable compliance track record.

